name: RecyclingWeek
0:
”Alexa, ask garbage buddy if it's recycling week”
”Alexa, ask garbage buddy if this week is recycling week”
”Alexa, ask garbage buddy if recycling is being picked up this week”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: garbage buddy
des: This skill tells you whether this week's garbage collection will include recycling pickup or not. It assumes that the recycling is picked up every other week.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
